## ğŸš€ Deploy Backend (Railway - Recommended)

1. **Create Railway Account:** https://railway.app/
2. **New Project â†’ Deploy from GitHub** (or manual upload)
3. **Add PostgreSQL:** Right click â†’ New â†’ Database â†’ PostgreSQL
4. **Set Environment Variables:**
   - Go to project â†’ Variables
   - Add all variables from your `.env.local`
5. **Deploy!**
   - Railway auto-deploys
   - Get your URL: `https://your-app.up.railway.app`

## ğŸ¨ Deploy Frontend (Netlify)

1. **Create folder with:**
   - `index.html`
   - `chat.html`

2. **Update chat.html API endpoint:**
   - Find all `/api/` calls
   - Change to your Railway URL: `https://your-app.up.railway.app/api/`

3. **Deploy to Netlify:**
   - Go to https://app.netlify.com/
   - Drag folder onto deploy zone
   - Done! Get URL: `https://your-site.netlify.app`

4. **Optional - Custom Domain:**
   - Netlify â†’ Domain Settings â†’ Add custom domain
   - Update DNS records as shown

